# Wolverine static handler codegen — committed for TypeLoadMode.Static, but not human-reviewed.
# The tree must stay in the repo (the host loads it with no runtime Roslyn compiler, and CI fails
# on a stale tree), but a single handler change regenerates 400+ files, which swamps PR review.
# linguist-generated=true collapses these in GitHub PR diffs by default and drops them from
# Copilot code review's per-PR file budget.
Wayd.Web/src/Wayd.Web.Api/Internal/Generated/WolverineHandlers/** linguist-generated=true
